Maximize
  3 x_medication_patches + 2 x_anti_biotic_creams
Subject To
  c1: 3 x_medication_patches + 5 x_anti_biotic_creams <= 400
  c2: 5 x_medication_patches + 6 x_anti_biotic_creams <= 530
  c3: x_medication_patches + x_anti_biotic_creams <= 100
  c4: x_anti_biotic_creams - 2.0 x_medication_patches >= 0
End